<h2>Default navigation controls</h2>
<p>Instructions for moving around the   model using the mouse and keyboard can also be found under the Help &gt; Controls menu in the 3D Data Viewer application</p>
  <h3>On-Screen Controls</h3>
  <table width="100%" border="1" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td valign="top" width="142"><strong>Pan:</strong></td>
        <td width="586"><img src="../images/navigation_onscreen_pan.png" alt="Onscreen Navigation - Pan" width="56" height="56" align="absmiddle" /> Click up/down/left/right buttons to pan in that direction.<br />        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td valign="top" width="142"><strong>Zoom:</strong></td>
        <td><img src="../images/navigation_onscreen_zoom.png" alt="Onscreen Navigation - Zoom" width="26" height="59" align="absmiddle" /> Click &quot;+&quot; or &quot;-&quot; buttons to zoom in or out.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td valign="top" width="142"><strong>Tilt: </strong></td>
        <td><p><img src="../images/navigation_onscreen_tilt.png" alt="Onscreen Navigation - Tilt" width="26" height="59" align="absmiddle" /> Click buttons to tilt down/up</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td valign="top"><strong>Rotate: </strong></td>
        <td><img src="../images/navigation_onscreen_rotate.png" alt="Onscreen Navigation - Rotate" width="26" height="59" align="absmiddle" />Click buttons to rotate left/right</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p>&nbsp;</p>
  <h3>Two Button Mouse 
  with Scroll Wheel and Keyboard</h3>
<table width="100%" border="1" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top" width="142"><strong>Pan:</strong></td>
      <td width="586"><ul>
        <li>Left mouse button click &amp; drag - all directions </li>
        <li>Single click left button to center screen</li>
        <li>Left/right/up/down arrows on the keyboard<br />
        </li>
      </ul></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top" width="142"><strong>Zoom:</strong></td>
      <td><ul>
        <li>Use the scroll wheel on the mouse to zoom in/out</li>
        <li> Middle mouse button/scroll wheel - click and drag - up and down</li>
        <li> Double click left/right button to zoom in/out and center screen</li>
        <li>Ctrl + up/down arrows on the keyboard<br />
        </li>
      </ul></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top" width="142"><strong>Tilt: </strong></td>
      <td><ul>
        <li>Right mouse button click &amp; drag - up and down </li>
        <li>'Page Up' and 'Page Down'  or shift + up/down arrows on the keyboard<br />
        </li>
      </ul></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top"><strong>Rotate: </strong></td>
      <td><ul>
        <li>Right mouse button click &amp; drag - left and right<br />
          Note: Crossing the   top and bottom half of the screen while rotating will change   direction.</li>
        <li>Shift + left/right arrows on the keyboard</li>
      </ul></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top"><strong>Stop Movement: </strong></td>
      <td><ul>
        <li>Spacebar</li>
      </ul></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top"><strong>Reset Heading: </strong></td>
      <td><ul>
        <li>N</li>
      </ul></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top"><strong>Reset Heading/Tilt: </strong></td>
      <td><ul>
        <li>R</li>
      </ul></td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
